Skin: Goku's skin remains the same, being Caucasian in tone with no noticeable blemishes. Height: His height is approximately 1.75 meters, staying the same as his normal form. Weight: His weight is approximately 62 kilograms, with no significant change from his base form. Musculature: His musculature looks slightly more defined and toned, but not excessively bulky. Clothing: He wears his characteristic orange and blue suit, but in his transformation to Super Warrior he is modified. The upper part of the suit now has a vertical white line that runs along the entire torso and widens at the shoulders, creating a kind of shoulder pads. The pants also feature a white vertical line, which ends at the top of the red boots. In summary, when Goku transforms into a "Super Warrior" with red hair, his appearance changes, although in essence he remains the same character.
